.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190622/59745536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190622%2F59745536&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=707a0437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190622%2F59745536&h=02b8a3ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190622/59745536</a>"},{"pid":"27642d7150d475f67d6be6a33cad669d0ce32d91","tid":1252580,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}